      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple though. i'm not just \"disappointed.\" i've lost millions that weren't even mine to lose. my parents put everything into my first startup and now i've bankrupted them too. every time i close my eyes i just see the looks on their faces. i feel like a ghost. like there's nothing left of me to actually \"try again\" with. there's just this massive, gaping hole where my life used to be.",
